    "en": {
      "title": "\"Democracy of the Freedom Party has been killed\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Chandrika Bandaranaike Kumaratunga said today (5) that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party, which was the most democratic party in the country after independence, has now killed its democracy.",
        "Also, the former president said that the party's policy has been destroyed and she said that she will continue to work for the people who protected the party's policies and the Sri Lanka Freedom Party.",
        "Mrs. Chandrika Bandaranaike Kumaratunga said this while speaking to the media after attending the opening ceremony of the New Lanka Freedom Party's party headquarters chaired by Member of Parliament Kumara Welgama."
      ],
